OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Les Budding
OL,5,FLes Budding, Age: 98, Royal Marines
OL,7,FInterviewed 23 February 2024
OL,9,FManning an Oerlikon anti-aircraft gun
OL,10,Fon a Landing Craft Flak on D-Day, Mr
OL,11,FBudding had been based in Portsmouth
OL,12,Ffor weeks leading up to the invasion
OL,13,Fand saw the massive build up of ships
OL,14,Fthere.
OL,16,F"A lot of them were tied up to bouys
OL,17,Fin the middle of the harbour," he said.
OL,19,F"Some couldn't even get into the
OL,20,Fharbour. They were outside tying up to
OL,21,Feach other.
