OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Les Budding
OL,5,F"We had five of those rocket ships at
OL,6,Four rear," he added.
OL,8,F"And they started letting the rockets
OL,9,Fgo and it was scary because flames
OL,10,Fwere shooting from the rear of them as
OL,11,Fthey were airborne, and there were
OL,12,Fthat many in the air they were
OL,13,Fcolliding with each other and diving
OL,14,Finto the sea and we were scared stiff
OL,15,Fthey would land on our upper deck
OL,16,Fbecause we had a lot of ammunition."
OL,18,FLes remembers enemy fire from German
OL,19,Fpositions close to where soldiers were
OL,20,Flanding.
