OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Les Budding
OL,5,FMr Budding said: "As (our troops) were
OL,6,Fhitting the beach we were opening fire
OL,7,Fat the top floor windows.
OL,9,F"There were lines of semi detached
OL,10,Fhouses all the way along the back of
OL,11,Fthe beach and at each upper window was
OL,12,Fsandbags and in the centre was either
OL,13,Fa machine gun or a mortar and they
OL,14,Fwere firing at our lads but we were
OL,15,Fhitting them.
OL,17,F"Our range was far greater.
OL,19,F"They were taking cover a lot of the
OL,20,Ftime when things were getting too hot
OL,21,Ffor them."
