OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Les Budding
OL,5,FSpeaking about how he feels about the
OL,6,Flandings now, Les said: "I get mixed
OL,7,Ffeelings.
OL,9,F"We were there to do a job and we did
OL,10,Fit successfully.
OL,12,F"These lads, they died, and all of
OL,13,Fthem that died you feel guilty that
OL,14,Fyou were left alive."
